      • getCheckinURLs

        @GET
 @Nullable
java.lang.Object getCheckinURLs(@Query @NotNull
                                                java.lang.String airlineCode,
                                                @Query @Nullable
                                                java.lang.String language,
                                                @NotNull
                                                kotlin.coroutines.Continuation<retrofit2.Response> p)

        Lists Check-in URLs. This operation allows retrieving a list of check-in urls based on the provider code and the language. ### Request example: What is the URL to my online check-in? GET https://test.api.amadeus.com/v2/reference-data/urls/checkin-links?airlineCode=BA ### Response Examples { \"warnings\": {\"status\":200,\"code\":10151,\"title\":\"DEFAULT LANGUAGE USED\",\"detail\":\"Language not available for this airline,default language applied\",\"source\":{\"parameter\":\"language\"}}, \"meta\": { \"count\": 1, \"links\": { \"self\": \"http://test.api.amadeus.com/v2/reference-data/urls/checkin-links?airlineCode=BA\" } }, \"data\": [ { \"type\": \"checkin-link\", \"id\": \"BAEN-GBAll\", \"href\": \"https://www.britishairways.com/travel/managebooking/public/en_ch?&bookingRef={PNR}&lastname={LAST}\", \"channel\": \"All\", \"parameters\": { \"LAST\": { \"description\": \"Passenger Last Name\", \"type\": \"string\" }, \"PNR\": { \"description\": \"Record Locator\", \"type\": \"string\", \"format\": \"(a-zA-Z|0-9){6}\" } } } ] } The endpoint is owned by defaultname service owner

        Parameters:
        airlineCode - Airline code following IATA or ICAO standard - e.g. 1X; AF or ESY IATA table codes ICAO airlines table codes (required)
        language - Check-in page language with one of the following patterns 'languageCode' (e.g. EN) or 'languageCode-IATAcountryCode' (e.g. en-GB). Default value is en-GB (used when required language is not available or when no value is specified). (optional)
        See Also:
        {\"status\":200,\"code\":10151,\"title\":\"DEFAULT LANGUAGE USED\",\"detail\":\"Language not available for this airline,default language applied\",\"source\":{\"parameter\":\"language\"}}, a-zA-Z, 0-9
